<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="264">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$L_xs" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/L_xs" class="zg-link" title="wfh SQ">wfh SQ</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cui-wu-la" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cui-wu-la" class="zg-link" title="莉莉乌拉">莉莉乌拉</a></span>
